OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775466313
OL,3,CFire destroys disused sporting
OL,4,Cpavilion - cause investigated
OL,6,FThe cause of a fire which badly
OL,7,Fdamaged a disused pavilion in
OL,8,FSwanscombe is being investigated.
OL,10,FCrews from eight fire engines attended
OL,11,Fthe scene after flames were spotted
OL,12,Fcoming from the building at Broomfield
OL,13,FRecreation Ground.
OL,15,FThe fire broke out shortly before
OL,16,F3.40pm on Saturday April 4th, and
OL,17,Fcrews spent three hours bringing it
OL,18,Funder control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
