PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775466313
OL,3,CFire destroys disused sporting
OL,4,Cpavilion - cause investigated
OL,6,FThe building was closed two years ago
OL,7,Fbecause it was deemed to be beyond
OL,8,Fcost-effective repair.
OL,10,FPlans to construct a new clubhouse and
OL,11,Fchanging facilities are currently on
OL,12,Fhold because of concerns about the
OL,13,F#1.6 million predicted costs.
OL,15,FCllr Dawn Johnstone, mayor of the town
OL,16,Fcouncil and chair of the Swanscombe
OL,17,Fand Greenhithe Residents Association,
OL,18,Fposted an update on Facebook on
OL,19,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
