PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775466313
OL,3,CFire destroys disused sporting
OL,4,Cpavilion - cause investigated
OL,6,FShe said: "As you all are probably
OL,7,Faware, the fire brigade was called to
OL,8,Fthe old Swanscombe pavilion in
OL,9,FBroomfield Park on Saturday afternoon.
OL,11,F"They arrived promptly and contained
OL,12,Fthe situation.
OL,14,F"On visiting the person in charge of
OL,15,Fthe firefighters, I was told that the
OL,16,Fhall end was set alight, most likely
OL,17,Farson. The police will be informed.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
