OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775466313
OL,3,CFire destroys disused sporting
OL,4,Cpavilion - cause investigated
OL,6,F"All is now under control except that,
OL,7,Fas part of the building has a two-
OL,8,Flayer roof, and smoke is getting stuck
OL,9,Fin between them, they are removing the
OL,10,Fskirting round the roof and are
OL,11,Fdamping down that area.
OL,13,F"The council security contractor is
OL,14,Finvolved and, where necessary and
OL,15,Fpossible, will make the building safe.
OL,16,FThe fire officer and security have my
OL,17,Fnumber if I can help further.
OL,19,F"At this stage, it is not anticipated
OL,20,Fthat this will have any impact on the
OL,21,Fcurrent plans to build a new pavilion."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@gO]
